Column.Name: Description
Column.Display: When UNSAccount (Delinea account) gets assigned a person - assign Department folder and Title folder to that account.
Column.Value: When UNSAccount (Delinea account) gets assigned a person - assign Department folder and Title folder to that account.

Column.Name: Description
Column.Display: Assigns UNSAccountB to UNSGroupB depending on the Person primary Department. ObjectGUID UNSGroupB must already be there from Delinea sync.
Column.Value: Assigns UNSAccountB to UNSGroupB depending on the Person primary Department. ObjectGUID UNSGroupB must already be there from Delinea sync.

Column.Name: Description
Column.Display: Assigns UNSAccountB to UNSGroupB depending in the Identity Title
Column.Value: Assigns UNSAccountB to UNSGroupB depending in the Identity Title

Column.Name: ValueTemplate
Column.Display: Dim deptName = $FK(UID_Person).FK(UID_Department).DepartmentName$ Dim folderType = "Department Folder" Value = Connection.GetSingleProperty("UNSGroupB", "UID_UNSGroupB", "cn = '" + deptName + "' AND GroupType = '" + folderType + "' AND UID_UNSRootB = '" + $UID_UNSRootB$ + "'")
Column.Value: Dim deptName = $FK(UID_Person).FK(UID_Department).DepartmentName$ Dim folderType = "Department Folder" Value = Connection.GetSingleProperty("UNSGroupB", "UID_UNSGroupB", "cn = '" + deptName + "' AND GroupType = '" + folderType + "' AND UID_UNSRootB = '" + $UID_UNSRootB$ + "'")

Column.Name: ValueTemplate
Column.Display: Dim titleName = $FK(UID_Person).Title$ Dim folderType = "Title Folder" Value = Connection.GetSingleProperty("UNSGroupB", "UID_UNSGroupB", "cn = '" + titleName + "' AND GroupType = '" + folderType + "' AND UID_UNSRootB = '" + $UID_UNSRootB$ + "'")
Column.Value: Dim titleName = $FK(UID_Person).Title$ Dim folderType = "Title Folder" Value = Connection.GetSingleProperty("UNSGroupB", "UID_UNSGroupB", "cn = '" + titleName + "' AND GroupType = '" + folderType + "' AND UID_UNSRootB = '" + $UID_UNSRootB$ + "'")
